  "short_description": "Race through a set of short dungeons, trying to collect the most treasures. The player who has the most coins at the end wins the game! Will you hoard your coins? Invest in stronger gear? Or perhaps try to win extra gold with one of the awards? Face off against friends or play against the computer!",
