  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/553a902ed4130e112ca3b1923d59865f.gif?t=1741125360\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/553a902ed4130e112ca3b1923d59865f.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is this game?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bachelairs is foremost a local multiplayer game where you race through a short set of dungeons. The goal is to collect the most coins, which can be done via collecting treasures, beating up monsters, investing in better gear or winning awards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/e2c2d195d7dab1939c985c7767a819c4.gif?t=1741125360\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/e2c2d195d7dab1939c985c7767a819c4.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Back story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A kingdom far away is in need of brave warriors to help them get rid of a dungeon problem. Therefore they organized a grand tournament! Bachelors from across the kingdom will enter the dungeons, fight the monsters and loot the treasures there. The one that collects the most coins will win the cup and gets to marry one of the princes or princesses (consented)! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/004c8f125e9910345f5c97b2b1acea5f.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/004c8f125e9910345f5c97b2b1acea5f.webm?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/004c8f125e9910345f5c97b2b1acea5f.mp4?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >each game takes about 10 - 15 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 different playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different cups with 4 different dungeon types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >over 50 different items that you can use, such as weapons and hats</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/dcf980375aaef675801af3f1cee99a6d.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/dcf980375aaef675801af3f1cee99a6d.mp4?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1741125360\" width=200 height=70 /></span>Sokpop makes many short games. Get one every month!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/15c5b38ee2d825615c58006adccd4ba8.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" width=450 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/15c5b38ee2d825615c58006adccd4ba8.webm?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/15c5b38ee2d825615c58006adccd4ba8.mp4?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/553a902ed4130e112ca3b1923d59865f.gif?t=1741125360\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/553a902ed4130e112ca3b1923d59865f.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is this game?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bachelairs is foremost a local multiplayer game where you race through a short set of dungeons. The goal is to collect the most coins, which can be done via collecting treasures, beating up monsters, investing in better gear or winning awards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/e2c2d195d7dab1939c985c7767a819c4.gif?t=1741125360\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/e2c2d195d7dab1939c985c7767a819c4.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Back story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A kingdom far away is in need of brave warriors to help them get rid of a dungeon problem. Therefore they organized a grand tournament! Bachelors from across the kingdom will enter the dungeons, fight the monsters and loot the treasures there. The one that collects the most coins will win the cup and gets to marry one of the princes or princesses (consented)! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/004c8f125e9910345f5c97b2b1acea5f.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" width=450 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/004c8f125e9910345f5c97b2b1acea5f.webm?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/004c8f125e9910345f5c97b2b1acea5f.mp4?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >each game takes about 10 - 15 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 different playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different cups with 4 different dungeon types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >over 50 different items that you can use, such as weapons and hats</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/dcf980375aaef675801af3f1cee99a6d.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/dcf980375aaef675801af3f1cee99a6d.mp4?t=1741125360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1741125360\" width=200 height=70 /></span>Sokpop makes many short games. Get one every month!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380/extras/15c5b38ee2d825615c58006adccd4ba8.poster.avif?t=1741125360\" width=450 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948380